*[[潍坊|潍坊]]：''早春园店（超市，2013年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aeonchina.com.cn/2013/operation/%E9%9D%92%E5%B2%9B%E6%B0%B8%E6%97%BA%E6%BD%8D%E5%9D%8A%E6%97%A9%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%AD%E5%BA%972%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%9B%E8%A3%85%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%9A/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-10-06 |archive-date=2019-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512031148/http://www.aeonchina.com.cn/2013/operation/%E9%9D%92%E5%B2%9B%E6%B0%B8%E6%97%BA%E6%BD%8D%E5%9D%8A%E6%97%A9%E6%98%A5%E5%9B%AD%E5%BA%972%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%9B%E8%A3%85%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%9A/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>-2015年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2015-01-14/890450.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009172554/http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2015-01-14/890450.html |archive-date=2016-10-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>）''
